      <h1 class="content-hero-title">Navigating the Experience</h1>
      <p class="content-hero-subtitle">Preparation determines the conditions; navigation determines what you do when you arrive. This guide covers the phenomenological arc of a psychedelic journey, working skillfully with difficult material, understanding ego dissolution, supporting others, and knowing when to seek help.</p>
